

SILA

   This is the plural form of siya.
   si·lá
   they

   Sila ang pangalawa.
   They are the second.

   Sila ay hindi nagsalita.
   They did not speak.

   Hindi sila nagsalita.
   They didn’t speak.

   Sila ang may problema!
   They’re the ones with a problem!

   Can also be used as a polite version for “you” ([66]ikaw).
